      "title": "Tricycle fare down",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that it has been decided to reduce the fee of 100 rupees charged for the second kilometer of three-wheelers to 90 rupees due to the reduction in fuel prices.",
        "There will be no change in the existing fare of Rs 100 for the first kilometer."
